idth=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557790/extras/b8d98f028e07621573950740eba89451.webm?t=1746723912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557790/extras/b8d98f028e07621573950740eba89451.mp4?t=1746723912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
